                15 VIAL4000-FILLER-OUTPUT        PIC X(166).

                15 VIAL4000-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT      PIC X(11500).

                15 VIAL4000-DB2-LOG.
                   20 VIAL4000-TABLE-NAME        PIC X(16).
